            <p>Windsor sits at Canada's southernmost point, directly across from Detroit — a geography that creates family law situations found nowhere else in Ontario. Chinese-Canadian families in Windsor often have <strong>US income, US bank accounts, US property, and custody arrangements that cross an international border</strong>. Miao He (何淼) serves Windsor clients by Zoom, with in-person court attendance in Windsor when required. LSO #83315K · China Bar Association Licensed.</p>
